articles.author: Richa Banka
articles.title: HC issues notice over trials exemption granted to Vinesh Phogat, Bajrang Punia - Hindustan Times
articles.description: Wrestlers Antim Panghal and Sujeet Kalkal moved the Delhi high court to challenge the exemption granted to Vinesh Phogat, Bajrang Punia from the Asian Games trials | Latest News Delhi
articles.content:
The Delhi high court on Thursday issued a notice to the Wrestling Federation of India (WFI) over the exemption granted to wrestlers Vinesh Phogat and Bajrang Punia from the Asian Games trials.
